sql:
SELECT name
FROM weapons
WHERE atk = (SELECT MAX(atk) FROM weapons);

external_knowledge:
- 'Effective' refers to a high kill-to-death ratio (KDR);
- 'Profitable' refers to a high profit margin (sell price - buy price);
- 'Cost to craft' refers to the total cost of materials required to craft the weapon.

- "reaped the highest average number of souls" refers to the average number of kills;
- "souls" are the players killed by the weapon;
- "the most lethal weapons" are the top 10 weapons with the highest average kills.

sql:
SELECT name, rarity
FROM weapons
ORDER BY rarity ASC;

SELECT name
FROM weapons
WHERE buy_price = (SELECT MAX(buy_price) FROM weapons);

